reviews.text:
I'm all aboard this train! Peanut Butter + Banana has always been one of my favorite profiles, but I've never really gotten "peanut butter" from vape before, just peanuts, until I tried this. The CAP VCv1 really gets in the mix to thicken up and smooth out those peanuts to give you a good essence of peanut butter. &#xD;
&#xD;
I didn't mix this 1:1 since I didn't have HS Peanut Butter, but FLV made a fine substitute. I also tried this swapping out the FA Banana for HS Banana @ 0.75% and was very pleased with the results. This is definitely one I'm glad I have on hand!
